《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
“外防输入”已是当前疫情防控重中之重。
"External defense input" has become the most important disease prevention and control.
海外累计确诊病例超过10万，世卫组织呼吁各国扩大监测范围。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases overseas exceeds 100,000, and WHO calls on countries to expand surveillance.
欧洲更多国家关闭边境文 |《财经》数据研究员 徐进图 |《财经》视觉中心编辑| 郝洲一、北京重启小汤山医院，严防境外疫情输入图1今日国内简述：国内3月16日报告累计确诊病例80881例，武汉新增1例。
More countries in Europe have closed borders with China. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
国内本地新增有望实现归零。
New domestic growth is expected to reach zero.
境外输入病例20例（北京9例，上海3例，广东3例，浙江1例，山东1例，广西1例，云南1例，陕西1例）。
There were 20 imported cases from abroad (9 in Beijing, 3 in Shanghai, 3 in Guangdong, 1 in Zhejiang, 1 in Shandong, 1 in Guangxi, 1 in Yunnan and 1 in Shaanxi).
中央应对新冠肺炎疫情工作领导小组16日召开会议，要求各地及时足额兑现防控一线人员补助，援鄂医务人员将分批撤离。
The 16-day meeting of the Leading Group for the Central Government's Response to the New Crown Pneumonia called for timely and full payment of subsidies to prevent and treat frontline personnel.
国家卫健委称，我国在外人员众多，境外留学生等重点群体回国意愿强烈，当前疫情防控形势出现重要变化。
According to the National Health Committee, China has a large number of foreign students, overseas students and other key groups strong willingness to return home, the current situation of disease prevention and control has changed significantly.
即日起，北京实行最严密的入境检疫。
From now on, Beijing will carry out the most stringent quarantine measures.
对所有境外进京人员进行14天的集中医学观察，费用自理。
All overseas visitors to Beijing will be under intensive medical observation for 14 days at their own cost.
北京小汤山医院于3月16日重新启用，将主要用于境外来（返）京人员中需筛查人员、疑似病例及轻型、普通型确诊患者的筛查和治疗。
The Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital, which was reopened on March 16, will be used mainly for screening and treatment of people who need to be screened, suspected cases and confirmed patients with mild or ordinary types of illness from abroad.
二、海外累计确诊病例超过10万，世卫组织开始远程办公图2新冠疫情在中国以外140多个国家和地区蔓延，累计确诊病例超过10万。
II. Cumulatively, more than 100,000 cases have been confirmed overseas, and WHO has begun to spread the new crown of telecommuting in over 140 countries and regions outside China, with a cumulative total of over 100,000 confirmed cases.
各国政府纷纷升级应对措施，数以亿计的民众被迫进入“禁足”式的居家生活模式。
Governments have escalated their response, forcing hundreds of millions of people into "no-go" lifestyles at home.
巴基斯坦确诊病例猛增三位数。
Confirmed cases surged to triple digits in Pakistan.
世卫组织总干事谭德塞呼吁所有国家应扩大检测范围，为所有怀疑个案作测试，因为“不能蒙着眼睛去打这场战争”。
WHO Director-General Lindsey calls on all countries to expand testing for all suspected cases, because "the war cannot be fought blindfolded."
世卫组织发言人塔里克·贾萨瑞维奇宣布，除关键人员外，3月16日起世卫组织日内瓦总部员工开始远程办公，新冠肺炎例行发布会也改为线上模式，发布会现场无媒体记者。
WHO spokesman Tariq Jasarevic announced that, in addition to key personnel, WHO headquarters staff in Geneva began telecommuting on 16 March, and the regular launch of Newcastle Pneumonia was changed to an online format, with no media coverage.
图3今天，小编把欧盟的线做了拆分。
Fig. 3 Today, the minor editor splits the lines of the EU.
意大利、西班牙、德国、法国、伊朗、美国为当前疫情最严重的六个国家，六个国家昨日新增确诊病例9998例，占全球新增病例总数的76.8%。
Italy, Spain, Germany, France, Iran and the United States were the six worst affected countries, with 9,998 new cases confirmed yesterday in six countries, accounting for 76.8 per cent of all new cases worldwide.
意、西、伊三国正处于拉锯阶段，德、法、美则处于起步阶段。
Italy, Spain and Iraq are in the process of sawing, while Germany, France and the United States are in the initial stages.
值得注意的是意大利的新增出现下降究竟是趋势改变，还是随机波动？有待今后几天数据确认。
It is worth noting whether the new decline in Italy is a change in trend or random fluctuations? It remains to be seen whether the data will be confirmed in the coming days.
三、美国日增近千病例，五角大楼出现37例确诊图4美国累计确诊升至4697例，累计死亡91例。
The number of confirmed cases in the Pentagon rose from 37 to 4,697, with a cumulative total of 91 deaths.
此外，美国五角大楼已出现37例确诊病例，美国国防部部长和副部长将被隔离。
In addition, there have been 37 confirmed cases at the Pentagon, and the secretary and deputy secretary of defense will be quarantined.
当地时间16日下午，美国白宫召开发布会，美国总统特朗普公布了更为严格的防疫指导意见，建议美国人今后15天避免10人以上的聚集，避免在餐馆、酒吧聚餐，避免探亲访友等。
President Trump, speaking at a White House news conference Tuesday afternoon, issued more stringent anti-epidemic guidelines, advising Americans to avoid gathering more than 10 people over the next 15 days, avoid eating in restaurants and bars and avoid visiting relatives and friends.
特朗普说，美国政府准备采取任何必要的措施。
Trump says the administration is prepared to take whatever steps are necessary.
根据目前情况，也许考虑在“热点地区”采取隔离、宵禁等举措，但暂不考虑在全国施行，“希望我们不用这样做（全国宵禁）。
Depending on the situation, measures such as isolation, curfews in "hot spots" might be considered, but not across the country for the time being. "I hope we don't have to."
图4.1美国依然精准地站在拟合线上。
Figure 4.1 The United States remains precisely on the fit line.
预计3月20日其累计病例会突破一万。
The cumulative number of cases is expected to exceed 10,000 by 20 March.
鉴于美国各州以及联邦政府日益重视，不断提高检测能力和防控等级，希望未来几天能起好的变化。
In the light of the growing interest of the states and the federal government in improving detection capabilities and control levels, it is hoped that positive changes will occur in the coming days.
当然更多人认为随着检测能力初步到位，短期内会使确诊数激增。
Of course, more people believe that with the initial detection capacity in place, the number of diagnoses will surge in the short term.
四、欧洲成新冠疫情世界中心图5欧盟委员会主席冯德莱恩16日表示，她提议对所有欧盟以外人员进入欧盟的非必要旅行进行限制，为期30天。
European Commission President Von Dreyne said Monday she proposed a 30-day limit on non-essential travel to the European Union for all non-EU nationals.
不过该提议将不会影响欧盟国家之间的旅行，但一些成员国已经纷纷“擅自决定”关闭了各自的边境。
But the proposal would not affect travel between EU countries, but some member states have already closed their borders "of their own accord."
目前26个申根区国家中的10个已开始实行边境控制。
Border controls are now in place in 10 of the 26 Schengen area countries.
自当地时间3月17日0时起，西班牙正式封锁陆地边境，只允许拥有西班牙国籍和本国长期居留者入境。
Since 0000 hours local time on 17 March, Spain has officially closed its land borders, allowing only Spanish nationals and permanent residents of the country to enter its territory.
西班牙将征用全国的私立医院和卫生机构，政府同时呼吁四年级的医学专业学生也加入到抗疫行动中来。
Spain will expropriate private hospitals and health facilities across the country, and the government is calling on medical students in the fourth grade to join the fight.
德国采取“从未见过的严厉措施”。
Germany has taken "never-seen draconian measures."
宣布禁止在教堂、清真寺和犹太教堂聚会，并命令关闭不必要的商店以及游乐场，但超市、银行、邮局、药店和加油站都将保持开放。
Meetings in churches, mosques and synagogues had been banned and unnecessary shops and playgrounds had been closed, but supermarkets, banks, post offices, pharmacies and gas stations would remain open.
美发室、建筑用品商店和自助洗衣店也将继续营业，确保“服务提供者和手工业者可以继续开展贸易”。
Hairdressing rooms, construction stores and laundries will also remain open, ensuring that "service providers and craftsmen can continue trading."
法国将关闭进入欧盟和申根区的边境30天，来自欧盟以外的人和非欧盟公民不能入境。
France will close its borders with the European Union and the Schengen area for 30 days, excluding people from outside the EU and non-EU citizens.
法国政府将从当地时间17日中午开始，限制法国人的出行。
The French government will restrict French travel from noon local time on the 17th.
只有购买食物，就医和工作才可以出行。
Only food purchases, medical treatment and work are allowed to travel.
为此，法国将动用10万警察和宪兵进行管制。
To that end, France will deploy 100,000 police and gendarmerie officers for that purpose.
启用法国军队运输患者。
French army is used to transport patients.
在疫情严重的阿尔萨斯地区，将建立一所战地医院。
A field hospital will be established in the heavily affected region of Alsace.
瑞士联邦主席西莫内塔·索马鲁加也在3月16日宣布瑞士进入“非常状态”。
The President of the Swiss Confederation, Simoneta Sommaruga, also declared a "state of emergency" in Switzerland on 16 March.
即日起至4月19日，瑞士所有餐厅、剧院、电影院和非必要的商业场所全部关闭。
From now until 19 April, all restaurants, theatres, cinemas and non-essential commercial premises in Switzerland were closed.
16日午夜，瑞士将在法国，德国，奥地利边境实施管控。
At midnight on the 16th, Switzerland will control the borders of France, Germany and Austria.
图5.1西欧五国还在指数拟合线的轨迹上，希望从今天（n39）起，红线能够向右穿越绿线。
Figure 5.1 The five Western European countries are also on the track of the exponential fitting line, hoping that from today (n 39) the red line will be able to cross the Green Line to the right.
即便如此，它们的总体病例数应该会超过意大利。
Even so, their total number of cases should exceed that of Italy.
如果趋势不改，预计这五国的合计新冠确诊病例将于4天后突破5万。
If the trend continues, the combined number of confirmed new cases in the five countries is expected to exceed 50,000 in four days.
图6意大利累计新冠肺炎确诊病例27980例，累计死亡病例2158例，病死率达到7.7%，这个数字远远高于全球平均3.7%的死亡率。
Fig. 6 The cumulative number of confirmed cases of Newly Coronary Pneumonia in Italy is 27980 and the cumulative number of deaths is 2,158, with a fatality rate of 7.7%, which is far higher than the global average of 3.7%.
图6.1意大利从n36开始显示明确向右变轨的迹象，说明病毒扩撒得到一定程度减缓。
Figure 6.1. Italy shows clear signs of right-wing re-orbiting, beginning with n-36, indicating that the spread of the virus has slowed to some extent.
我们用一条底数为2.2的指数线进行拟合，获得较好效果。
We use an index line with a base number of 2.2 to get a better result.
可以粗略理解为其有效传染数从3.7，降到了2.2（1是“拐点”）。
It can be roughly understood that its effective infectious number fell from 3.7 to 2.2 (1 being the "inflection point").
如果未来几天红线能够向右穿过绿线，说明传染数继续降低，那将是一个很好的征兆。
It would be a good sign if the red line were to cross the Green Line to the right in the coming days, indicating a continued decline in infections.
尽管如此，按现有趋势预计意大利病例总数将在5天后突破5万。
Nevertheless, current trends predict that the total number of cases in Italy will exceed 50,000 in five days.
意大利超高的病死率更令人困惑。
Italy's extremely high fatality rate is even more puzzling.
但愿这不是由大面积漏诊造成的。
Hopefully, this is not due to extensive missed diagnosis.
五、韩国再次推迟开学时间， 对所有旅客采取入境管制图7韩国政府17日决定将特别入境检疫程序的适用范围扩大至所有国家和地区，19日零时起入境韩国的所有旅客须走特别入境程序。
The ROK Government decided on the 17th day to extend the application of the special entry quarantine procedure to all countries and regions. All passengers entering the ROK from 0000 hours on the 19th day are subject to a special entry procedure.
韩国社会副总理兼教育部长官俞银惠3月17日要求全国范围内所有学校，包括幼儿园和中小学、高中，延期2周至4月6日开学，这是韩国第三次在全国范围内推迟学校开学，也是韩国首次4月份开学。
The Vice-Prime Minister and Minister of Education of the Republic of Korea, Yu Yinhui, requested on 17 March that all schools nationwide, including kindergartens and primary, secondary and high schools, be extended by two weeks until the start of the school year on 6 April, the third nationwide delay in the opening of schools and the first in South Korea in April.
六、伊朗完成1400万人排查，中国产试剂盒投入使用图8伊朗开展的全国动员计划，其派遣的30万支疫情排查小组已经在疫情最严重的省份开始工作，截至当地时间16日晚，已经完成了对1400万人的排查工作。
Iran completes 14 million checkups, Chinese test kits come into use Figure 8 Iran's national mobilization plan has sent 300,000 outbreak detection teams to work in the most affected provinces, and 14 million people had been screened by the end of the 16 night local time.
伊朗武装力量计划建立的“医疗卫生总部”也在按计划进行，军队宣布将在全国范围内建立1000处流动和固定医疗点，实行“早发现、早隔离”的防疫政策。
The planned establishment of a "medical and health headquarters" by the Iranian armed forces is also proceeding as planned, with the army announcing that it will establish 1,000 mobile and fixed medical stations nationwide and implement a policy of early detection and early isolation.
伊朗全国范围内的新冠肺炎检测中心已经从最初的几个增加到目前的50个，每个省份都可以及时进行核酸试剂检测和化验。
The number of new crest pneumonia testing centers nationwide has increased from the first few to 50 so far, with timely detection and testing of nucleic acid reagents in each province.
由中国红会志愿专家团带来的国产核酸试剂盒，也在之前通过了伊朗最权威的巴斯德实验室的平行检测，目前已经广泛派发并投入使用。
Nucleic acid test kits brought in by the Chinese Red Cross volunteer expert mission have also passed parallel tests at Iran's most authoritative Pasteur laboratory and are now widely distributed and in use.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】七、全球疫情数字速览：1、【国内非湖北地区复工率已超过90%】3月17日，国家发改委举行例行新闻发布会，新闻发言人孟玮介绍，全国规模以上工业企业复工率提高较快，除湖北等个别省份外，全国其他省（区、市）复工率均已超过90%，其中浙江、江苏、上海、山东、广西、重庆等已接近100%。
According to statistics released by the National Development and Reform Commission (NDRC) on February 28, 2007, the resumption rate of industrial enterprises above the national scale has increased by 90 percent, with Zhejiang, Jiangsu, Shanghai, Shandong, Guangxi and Chongqing provinces, a spokesman for the National Development and Reform Commission said.
2、【1350名囚犯越狱】3月16日，巴西4所监狱发生了数百名囚犯逃脱的事件。
2007-9-24 16: 53 [hide] Hundreds of prisoners escaped from four Brazilian prisons on March 16.
据悉，引发这些犯人集体越狱的原因是，由于新冠病毒疫情的暴发，原定于17日进行的放风活动被取消。
It is reported that the group of prisoners escaped because of the outbreak of the New Crown Virus outbreak, scheduled to take place on the 17th of the wind was cancelled.
与此同时，位于圣保罗州特雷门贝、费利斯港、米兰多波利斯、陶巴特等地多所监狱也发生了囚犯出逃与反抗事件，一些留在监狱里的囚犯开始纵火烧床垫、搞破坏。
At the same time, escapes and rebellions took place in several prisons in the State of São Paulo, including Trembe, Puerto Ferris, Milandopolis and Tabat, and some of the prisoners who remained in the prison began burning mattresses and damaging them.
逃犯的确切人数仍在统计之中。
The exact number of fugitives is still being counted.
此前媒体报道至少1350名囚犯逃离了监狱。
Earlier, media reports indicated that at least 1,350 prisoners had fled the prison.
3、【5.1万个试剂盒出口】据韩联社报道，韩国青瓦台表示，3月17日向阿联酋紧急出口了5.1万个新型冠状病毒检测试剂盒。
3, 2007-9-24 16: 16 [51,000 test kits] South Korea's Qingwadai said it had sent an emergency export of 51,000 new coronavirus test kits to the UAE on March 17, 2007.
这是韩国首次对外出口新冠病毒检测试剂盒。
This is the first time South Korea exported a new crown virus detection kit.
青瓦台称，迄今为止共有17个国家通过政府渠道正式请求韩方供货，韩国当天向其中交期最短的阿联酋出口了首批试剂盒。
So far, 17 countries have formally requested Korean supplies through government channels, with South Korea exporting the first batch of kits to the UAE, which has the shortest delivery period, according to Qingwadai.
小结：境外留学生等重点群体回国意愿强烈，当前国内疫情防控形势出现重要变化。
Summary: Overseas students and other key groups have a strong desire to return home, the current situation of domestic epidemic prevention and control has changed significantly.
海外累计确诊病例超过10万，世卫组织呼吁各国扩大监测范围。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases overseas exceeds 100,000, and WHO calls on countries to expand surveillance.
欧洲更多国家关闭边境。
More countries in Europe are closing their borders.
